    <p>This one-hour ses­sion is or­gan­ised by the Sin­ga­pore Chi­nese Cul­tural Cen­tre and Drum Feng, an award-win­ning home-grown per­cus­sion en­sem­ble. Par­tic­i­pants will learn ba­sic per­cus­sion no­ta­tion, which is com­monly used by Drum Feng and many other per­cus­sion prac­ti­tion­ers around the world. There are three lev­els of classes – be­gin­ner, in­ter­me­di­ate and ad­vanced – which are suit­able for those aged 13 and older.</p>
    <p>WHERE: Sin­ga­pore Chi­nese Cul­tural Cen­tre, 1 Straits Boule­vard</p>
